This is the Jehovah's Witness Audio Bible which i have compiled from there Website.  &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.jw.org/en/publications/bible/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.jw.org/en/publications/bible/&lt;/a&gt; 

Basically they dont give out a DVD or CD version anymore, you have to get it from there website, unfortunately they are zipped and it is broken up in to many small books which is kind of awkward to download if you want to use it in the car or i-pod. 

So i Downloaded them, put them all together in one neat package here. 

Even if you are not a JW, this is a good bible, and the Audio narrator is easily one of the best for an audio bible. 

Well worth having.
